<section class="content">
  <div class="col-1">
    <h2>Hi, I'm Andrea.</h2>
    <p class="nickname">You can call me Andi.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="col-2">
    <%= image_tag("amignolo-profile-web.jpg", :class => "bio") %>

    <p>Over the last two decades I've had a pretty winding career path: testing video games, overseeing the digital side of Free Speech TV, teaching business English in Japan, and building product at multiple tech start-ups with two exits and one currently at unicorn status. Since 2020 I've been an executive coach working with unconventional leaders and teams including non-founder executives, global management teams, and emerging leaders.</p>

    <p>I work one-on-one with clients, coach executive teams, run group coaching programs, and design leadership development curriculum for organizations.</p>

    <p>I write a monthly newsletter called Kitchen Party that explores the intersection of leadereship, business, psychology, and design. I'm also the President of the <%= link_to('Interaction Design Association', 'https://ixda.org/') %> and run an experimental ontological design studio, <%= link_to('P N T S . U S', 'https://pnts.us/') %>.</p>

    <p>Outside of coaching I am a <%= link_to('dedicated meditator', 'https://realizationprocess.org') %>, <%= link_to('occasional investor', 'https://angel.co/u/pnts') %>, amateur chef, and <%= link_to('budding martial artist', 'https://plumblossom.net/ChoyLiFut/') %>.</p>

  </div>
