    <p>At a glance, people I work with tend to be:</p>

    <ul class="bullets">
      <li>Non-founder executives - C-level, EVP, SVP, VP</li>
      <li>Executive teams</li>
      <li>Global management teams</li>
      <li>Pre-seed to IPO start-ups & scale-ups</li>
      <li>Social entrepreneurs</li>
      <li>Senior ICs (staff, prinicpal)</li>
      <li>Emerging leaders (senior manager - director level) in design, product management, and engineering</li>
